text: Francisco Uranga (born 1905, date of death unknown) was an Argentine swimmer. He competed in two events and the water polo tournament at the 1928 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1905 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Argentine male swimmers Category:Argentine male water polo players Category:Olympic swimmers of Argentina Category:Olympic water polo players of Argentina Category:Swimmers at the 1928 Summer Olympics Category:Water polo players at the 1928 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
